UKHALA ngonya lwamaphoyisa umndeni womlisa okuthiwa ushonele esiteshini samaphoyisa saseMooi River ngoLwesine emini,  okuthiwa amshaye ngoba  efuna agonyuluko ngokubanjwa kwenkunzi iloli   elithwala utshwala. UMnuz Swelihle Ngubane ( 31) wakwaGezubuza, eLandskop  okuthiwa ushone ngemva kokuthi amaphoyisa ezame ukumgonyilukisa iqiniso, kulandela ukuthi  yena nomshayeli weloli besolwe ngumnikazi walo ngokupheka itulo lokubanjwa inkunzi kwalo. Kuthiwa uNgubane nomshayeli bebeya eMooi River beyothulula utshwala ngenkathi bekhonjwa ngesibhamu omunye umsolwa abagcine beboshwe naye. Umalume kamufi, uMnuz Xolani Ngongoma, uthe basola ukuthi umshayeli obehlele itulo lokubanjwa kweloli njengoba kunguye olimisile ngesikhathi bekhonjwa. “ Sifisa ukuthi amaphoyisa athathelwe izinyathelo ngokubulala umshana. Ubeqala kulo nyaka ukuthunywa nomshayeli umshana futhi ubengasayizwisisi eyokubasiza njengoba ebeke asho ngobungozi bokuhamba nabo. Umsolwa obanjiwe kumele akhulume iqiniso njengoba umuntu obekumele asize umshayeli ngalolu suku ekhethe ukungayi emsebenzini,” kubeka uNgongoma. Elandisa, uthe basitshelwe ukuthi ngesikhathi  umshayeli emisa iloli,  kungene iqulu lamadoda abezifihle ubuso baqoqa amakesi abegcwele utshwala kanti umnikazi walo uyababuka kumakhamera wayesethinta amaphoyisa afike abopha umufi, umshayeli nomsolwa oyedwa. Abanye abasolwa kuthiwa babalekile. Uthe ngemva kokuthi umsolwa ethe itulo lokubanjwa kweloli balikhande noNgubane, amaphoyisa abe esesebenzisa izindlela zokuthi ahlanze iqiniso nokuthiwa yikhona okuholele ekutheni ashone. Okhulumela i- Ipid, uNksz Ndileka Cola, uthe usalinde umbiko ogcwele mayelana nalolu daba, okuze kwashaya isikhathi sokushicilela engaphundulanga. 